   <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mostly written as a note to myself while I’m configurering my Amiga 600HD.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;dir&lt;/code&gt; -  directory&lt;/li&gt;
